#: ../../language/error_codes/E0047.md:1
msgid "E0047"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0047.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `invalid_mbti`"
msgstr "警告名称：`invalid_mbti`"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0047.md:5
msgid "Invalid mbti file."
msgstr "无效的 mbti 文件。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0047.md:7
msgid ""
"This warning name is kept in the warning table for invalid `.mbti` files,"
" but the current interface parser reports syntax errors in `.mbti` files "
"as [`E3100`](E3100.md)."
msgstr ""
"此警告名称保留在 warning table 中，用于无效的 `.mbti` 文件；但当前接口解析器会将 `.mbti` 文件中的语法错误报告为 "
"[`E3100`](E3100.md)。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0047.md:11
msgid ""
"If you see an invalid interface warning from a tool that still uses this "
"warning entry, regenerate the `.mbti` file (or fix the tool that produced"
" it) so that the interface matches the current compiler version."
msgstr ""
"如果某个工具仍使用此 warning entry 并报告了无效接口警告，请重新生成 `.mbti` "
"文件（或修复生成它的工具），使接口匹配当前编译器版本。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0047.md:15
msgid ""
"This page has no checked source example because current invalid `.mbti` "
"diagnostics are documented and monitored under E3100."
msgstr "此页面没有受检查的源码示例，因为当前无效 `.mbti` 诊断已在 E3100 下记录并监控。"
